                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Real-time embedded software for reliable device operation</p>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                    <li>• Real-time operating systems (FreeRTOS, Zephyr)</li>
                    <li>• Device drivers and HAL development</li>
                    <li>• Communication protocols (USB, CAN, Ethernet)</li>
                    <li>• Safety-critical software (IEC 62304)</li>
                    <li>• Over-the-air update systems</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8 hover:shadow-md hover:border-orange-200 transition-all duration-200">
