                    <li>• Automated testing frameworks and CI/CD</li>
                    <li>• Hardware-in-the-loop (HIL) testing</li>
                    <li>• EMC testing and signal integrity validation</li>
                    <li>• FDA 510(k) and IEC 62304 compliance</li>
